Uropod (
Fig. 29B
). Each lamella with four claws and one short proximal spine dorsally. Both lamella with three spines and three rows of setae on anteroventral surface.

Female copulatory organ (
Fig. 29B
). Female spermatheca possessing finely corrugated structure in lateral view.
